{"tid":1919662,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"虛驚！安巴比新冠病毒測試呈陰性","createTime":"2020-03-11T02:36:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T03:33:50.000Z","uid":351466,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b5de1ae7ceb4aa6b179c532bef1aaf5da0fa0aad","tid":1919662,"uid":351466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T02:36:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=28799401185\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.now.com%2Fhome%2Fnews%2Fdetails%3Fid%3D28799401185&d=Pl33APIo1S6IjQ3qGLZsPUyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=4449cb02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=28799401185</a><br />\n<br />\n巴黎聖日耳門球星安巴比因喉嚨痛缺席操練，幸好新型冠狀病毒測試呈陰性。<br />\n新型冠狀病毒在歐洲大肆爆發，射手安巴比（Kylian Mbappe）近兩日因喉嚨痛和發燒缺席操練，惹來感染恐怖病毒的驚雲，幸好周二接受病毒測試後，證實為陰性，僅屬一場虛驚。<br />\n據悉，雖然安巴比沒有感染病毒，但周三歐聯16強次回合對多蒙特未必能披甲，有指他最多只會擔任後備，皆因連日來因病告假，體能狀態存疑。巴黎聖日耳門首回合負1:2，周三將在主場閉門迎戰求平反敗局。<br />\n巴黎聖日耳門教練杜慈周二說：「安巴比昨天病了，今天則因喉嚨痛請病假。明天（周三）早上才知道他的情況。」"},{"pid":"6445b918def49437783d8e78d4ea51c03d70ac1a","tid":1919662,"uid":72228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T02:41:11.000Z","msg":"有假陰性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10af108fcb973f4d495cdd6768c65fb2eb916933","tid":1919662,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T02:49:37.000Z","msg":"驚多蒙特驚到咁樣"},{"pid":"8dacdfbba4d4a47f13d052b080abc3907f7f85c9","tid":1919662,"uid":14188,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T03:33:50.000Z","msg":"喉嚨痛都可以請病假？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}